{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sort of, like, escaping out from this little [INAUDIBLE], from [INAUDIBLE], and started walking back to Hanaczow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I stayed there a few days again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Hanaczow?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, also.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also a [INAUDIBLE] you know, like outdoors, you know, where they had these stacks with hay and straw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was another family there, that they were also, like-- they live still in Hanaczow, Jewish people, but they were also, like, in the Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they took me in for a couple days, and there was sort of like a place in their little house, their little room, that I could hide.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they kept me there, I think, also a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I went back to the concentration camp again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, bundled myself up, and this was, again, about eight miles, nine miles, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I walked there, and I came there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they tried to push me back into the, to this, to be a part of the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I remained there till a week before they liquidated it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was it like, the concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Working every day, in the field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] came to springtime, we started planting and, and making ready the, the soil, and, and working every day there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many times, we were afraid to go back to this house to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But being that we worked on the fields, sometimes we-- you know, if nobody knew, we stayed there during the night too, that we wouldn't go [INAUDIBLE] because it was [INAUDIBLE] always a frightening feeling.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is they going to come during the night or something?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going to finish us off.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
